•	selgitab turunduskompleksi kujunemist, -juhtimist, mõjureid ja omavahelisi seoseid, koostab turundusplaani.

subject.outcomesEn:
Student who has passed the subject:
• demonstrates in-depth knowledge in the field of marketing;
• analyzes the impact of marketing activities on the company's operations and assesses the company's opportunities and threats in the market;
• analyzes the target market, target groups and consumer purchasing behavior and the factors influencing it and the purchasing decision process;
• segments and positions the market and defines marketing goals and strategies based on the competitive situation;
• explains the formation, management, influencers and interrelationships of the marketing complex, prepares a marketing plan.

subject.outcomesEt:
