• analyzes the business situation and its situation in the economy;
• demonstrates in-depth knowledge related to entrepreneurship in accordance with the Estonian economic space and legislation;
• compares business forms and selection principles;
• knows the principles of starting and operating a business and the processes at the level of starting and operating a business.

subject.outcomesEt:
