●	analüüsib äriplaanis toodet, ärikeskkonda, turgu, kliente ning konkurente; 
●	koostab tegevuskava äriidee elluviimiseks ja koostab investeeringute plaani ja finantsprognoosid;
●	koostab turundus- ja personaliplaani ning analüüsib äriidee elluviimisega seonduvaid riske.

subject.outcomesEn:
The student having passed the course:
•	develops a business idea for the start-up or existing enterprise;
•	in their business plan analyses the product, business environment, market, customers and competitors;
•	prepares the action plan to carry out the business idea and writes the investment plan and provides financial forecasts;
•	prepares the marketing and personnel plan and analyses the risks concerning the implementation of the business idea.

